ame-meets-former-us-vice-president-al-gore/">Okyeame Kwame meets former US Vice President Al Gore </a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/nigerian-north-west-state-governors-visit-african-development-bank-to-boost-cooperation/">Nigerian North West State Governors visit African Development Bank to boost cooperation</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/vaal-real-estate-ghana-maximises-your-returns-the-significance-of-roi-in-real-estate-investments/">Vaal Real Estate Ghana maximises your returns; the significance of ROI in real estate investments</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/my-five-daughters-were-killed-by-a-trailer-but-im-yet-to-get-justice-father-cries/">My five daughters were killed by a trailer but I&#8217;m yet to get justice &#8211; Father cries</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/akontombra-nkwanta-residents-lament-poor-telecommunication-network-in-their-community/">Akontombra Nkwanta residents lament poor telecommunication network in their community</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/ndc-promises-lean-govt-to-reserve-resources-for-assembly-members-allowances/">NDC promises lean gov&#8217;t to reserve resources for assembly members’ allowances</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/lets-put-in-effort-to-ensure-our-music-is-heard-globally-shatta-wale/">Let’s put in effort to ensure our music is heard globally &#8211; Shatta Wale</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/national-basketball-association-nba-africas-first-original-docuseries-born-bred-premieres-on-the-nba-app/">National Basketball Association (NBA) Africa’s First Original Docuseries “Born &amp; Bred” Premieres on the NBA App</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/all-set-for-guinness-ghana-dj-awards-on-november-25/">All set