ash/">2026 WCQ: ‘Every game is difficult whether home or away’ &#8211; Chris Hughton ahead of Comoros clash</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/network-international-appoints-mpho-sadiki-as-group-managing-director-merchant-solutions-for-africa/">Network International appoints Mpho Sadiki as Group Managing Director – Merchant Solutions for Africa</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/appointment-of-party-boys-worrying-clogsag/">Appointment of &#8216;party boys&#8217; worrying – CLOGSAG</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/dominic-obour-from-obscurity-to-limelight-the-rise-of-dmb/">Dominic Obour: From obscurity to limelight &#8211; The rise of DMB</a></li><li class="mostrecent_btf"><a href="https://www.myjoyonline.com/cedi-to-record-single-digit-depreciation-against-dollar-in-2024-eiu/">Cedi to record single-digit depreciation against dollar in 2024 – EIU</a></li></ul></div>
